com.vmware.apputils
Class Catalog

java.lang.Object
  com.vmware.apputils.Catalog

public final class Catalog
extends java.lang.Object

Java representation of the entity relationship specification for the QueryList API method. It provides methods to query which relationship combinations are supported, what properties are returned in each case and the type information for those properties.
